  "body": "Reproduction steps\r\n  1. clone this [project](https://github.com/cds-amal/psychic-octo-parakeet)\r\n  2. start `ganache-cli` in a separate terminal\r\n  3. run the tests: `truffle test`\r\n  4. grab a transaction from ganache's output\r\n  5. run the debugger with the compile-tests flag: `truffle debug --compile-tests <txn>`\r\n\r\nI was able to reproduce this on both WSL and Arch. See arch session below\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n$ use-truffle-core\r\n$ lsb_release -a\r\nLSB Version:    1.4\r\nDistributor ID: Arch\r\nDescription:    Arch Linux\r\nRelease:        rolling\r\nCodename:       n/a\r\n\r\n$ truffle version\r\nTruffle (unbundled) (core: 5.1.60)\r\nSolidity v0.5.16 (solc-js)\r\nNode v10.22.1\r\nWeb3.js v1.2.9\r\n\r\n\r\n$ truffle test\r\n\r\nCompiling your contracts...\r\n===========================\r\n> Compiling ./contracts/Dummy.sol\r\n> Compiling ./contracts/Migrations.sol\r\n> Compiling ./test/TestDummy.sol\r\n> Artifacts written to /tmp/test--7948-6Pksjlvts5pY\r\n> Compiled successfully using:\r\n   - solc: 0.5.16+commit.9c3226ce.Emscripten.clang\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n  TestDummy\r\n    ✓ testTargetIsInitialized (54ms)\r\n\r\n  Contract: Dummy\r\n    ✓ should assert true\r\n\r\n\r\n  2 passing (4s)\r\n\r\n$ truffle debug --compile-tests 0x38e676885fb0e18f2191d4bb3ae256ecd77d6cf827d7617369d94d59db03384f\r\nStarting Truffle Debugger...\r\n⠹ Compiling your contracts...Error: ENOENT: no such file or directory, scandir '/home/amal/dev/txlog/truffle-test-template/build/contracts'\r\n    at Object.readdirSync (fs.js:790:3)\r\n    at Truffle.<anonymous> (/home/amal/work/truffle/packages/resolver/lib/sources/truffle/index.ts:20:53)\r\n    at Generator.next (<anonymous>)\r\n    at fulfilled (/home/amal/work/truffle/packages/resolver/dist/lib/sources/truffle/index.js:5:58)\r\nTruffle (unbundled) (core: 5.1.60)\r\nNode v10.22.1\r\n\r\n```",
